code: @Override public void sent(Session session, Message message, Destination destination) {     if (exchange != null) {         String id = getJMSMessageID(message).         if (id != null) {             if (exchange.hasOut()) {                 exchange.getOut().setHeader("JMSMessageID", id).             } else {                 exchange.getIn().setHeader("JMSMessageID", id).             }         }     } }
